name: Overgrown [GB][Unfinished]
description:
Sadly unfinished GBJam 10 Game. Made with GBDK20. State of development post gamejam is currently unknown.

Current state: You can only navigate the main menu, jump around, fall through the level by holding down. And surrender by pressing SELECT + START

Source code can be found here:

https://github.com/KuroPSPiso/Overgrowth-GBJAM10
